data.title: Jamie Yeo - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Jamie Yeo: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Television presenter best known for her hosting duties with the Star Sports Network, including the soccer shows Castrol Football Crazy and Football Extra. She previously spent several years as a full-time radio DJ for 987FM.

Before Fame

She attended Fairfield Methodist Primary School and Nanyang Girls' High School in Singapore. She later moved to Dayton, Ohio, where she lived for four years.

Trivia

In addition to her sports work, she has hosted the travel and lifestyle show Inside Singapore from Insider.

Family Life

She was married to radio host Glenn Ong from 2004 to 2009 and Thorsten Nolte from 2010 to 2015. She has children named Alysia and Luke.
